Z","msg":"一般你google dsm5 就睇到有咩point <br />\n<br />\n最簡便就睇9個point<br />\n<br />\n一整天大部分時間都不快樂<br />\n興趣減少<br />\n體重或食慾下降<br />\n失眠（或嗜睡）<br />\n思考動作變得緩慢<br />\n整天沒活力病懨懨<br />\n覺得活的沒意思（沒價值感或罪惡感）<br />\n無法專注或決斷<br />\n有自殺念頭<br />\n<br />\n9個最少中5個 而一定要中第1or第2<br />\n又last左兩星期以上 就會懷疑有major depressive disorder"},{"pid":"737f16915a162b73ae68e1666cd11af0dc1271b4","tid":1673934,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5992e3bf97267ee21fafcf1c509ab610c16820","tid":1673934,"uid":235619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08beb29ced4e1036186d7845b5991f54eb33e110","tid":1673934,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3ec42afc3c16bce4a8524ec0d15f68f662c7c2","tid":1673934,"uid":235619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:51:21.000Z","msg":"我諗係10月開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"問多句 大致日常生活有冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n近排最大既壓力除左場運動 仲有冇一個明確主因？ e.g. 分手"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"事業，學業，愛情，親情，都不順"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:03:55.000Z","msg":"但會唔會出現冇動力到番工番學都做唔到？"},{"pid":"c9185a56aaf2f63abb1f17b6149464202cfee0d1","tid":1673934,"uid":2003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e5992e3bf97267ee21fafcf1c509ab610c16820","tid":1673934,"uid":235619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08beb29ced4e1036186d7845b5991f54eb33e110","tid":1673934,"uid":49979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e3ec42afc3c16bce4a8524ec0d15f68f662c7c2","tid":1673934,"uid":235619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:51:21.000Z","msg":"我諗係10月開始"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"問多句 大致日常生活有冇問題？<br />\n<br />\n近排最大既壓力除左場運動 仲有冇一個明確主因？ e.g. 分手"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"事業，學業，愛情，親情，都不順"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"太多事困擾住你啦<br />\n你壓力太大<br />\n有冇邊啲事情係可以解決到？ <br />\n解決左先，咁就少樣煩惱"},{"pid":"3e1039aed9ea8b0fd449035e707eaf353f903c5